{"tid":2121263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得而家好多人口語講「然後」兩個字","createTime":"2020-07-23T08:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T08:10:03.000Z","uid":288455,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2145975fe68c07491da3df779fac0f93adf70b5b","tid":2121263,"uid":288455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:01:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">預咗被人瘋狂負皮</span><br />\n「然後」兩個字絕對正確，由細用到大，但呢個詞好多時只係用喺書面語。<br />\n記得細個嗰陣（大約廿年前)，通常口語都係會講「跟住」同「之後」，「然之後」都成日聽，但好少可聽到人就咁講「然後」，但唔知幾時開始，成日聽到人係咁講「然後」，仲要「然後」前，「然後」後，好似無咗「跟住」一詞咁。<br />\n有無人同我一樣覺得啲人講「然後」好奇怪？"},{"pid":"4a0871a04a4a3d6af5337eee217c4d5d61ba8b52","tid":2121263,"uid":97840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86c2d0331ff746c43b7f98e2a2c4048f6b51614f","tid":2121263,"uid":308732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:05:09.000Z","msg":"然後就冇然後"},{"pid":"3ee7e66dcf7facab8344c8f2eebd207a8febf924","tid":2121263,"uid":28763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:05:31.000Z","msg":"然後 比 跟住 有多d 因果關係既感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d262f4113319c4766ac2fea0238e6bc7f2bf8d2c","tid":2121263,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:05:52.000Z","msg":"約定俗成"},{"pid":"a286c1eb4a89b66ad310d274a8cfeecd22a3ea23","tid":2121263,"uid":30836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:05:58.000Z","msg":"你開咗呢個po 然後又預咗俾人負皮 算唔算on9?"},{"pid":"23352bf142034de49e840f48d755c5997fdfe5a3","tid":2121263,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:06:16.000Z","msg":"同「確定」一樣<br />\n土炮跟本唔會咁講"},{"pid":"66f11c1e50f429c1a489ce5579a7679eb66b8d47","tid":2121263,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:07:58.000Z","msg":"啲女最鍾意講跟住<br />\n<br />\nXXYYZZ 跟住XXYYZZ跟住跟住跟住跟住跟住跟住"},{"pid":"de2c65b1b5b3caad7ae04